{"id":13832,"date":"2022-09-27T09:56:52","date_gmt":"2022-09-27T02:56:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=13832"},"modified":"2022-10-01T09:57:40","modified_gmt":"2022-10-01T02:57:40","slug":"loat-xe-dien-binh-dan-co-pham-vi-hoat-dong-tot-nhat","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/loat-xe-dien-binh-dan-co-pham-vi-hoat-dong-tot-nhat\/","title":{"rendered":"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"article__sapo cms-desc\">Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc EV d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 khi ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf ch\u00fang l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, d\u00e0n xe \u0111i\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u00f2n mang gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh &#8220;ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng&#8221; nh\u01b0ng di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u00e0i cho m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n s\u1ea1c.<\/div>\n<div class=\"article__body cms-body\">\n<p><strong>10. Mazda MX-30 (160,9 km)<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/mazda-mx-30-red-in-the-city-5115.png\" data-desc=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" data-index=\"0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/mazda-mx-30-red-in-the-city-5115.png\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1ea3nh 1\" data-image-id=\"3324296\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"486\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/mazda-mx-30-red-in-the-city-5115.png\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Mazda \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebf t\u1ea1o chi\u1ebfc EV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 MX-3. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t 100 d\u1eb7m (160,9 km) cho m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n s\u1ea1c, MX-30 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb 1-3 ng\u00e0y trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<p>Chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb pin hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t cao, cho ph\u00e9p n\u00f3 s\u1ea1c r\u1ea5t nhanh, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng pin t\u1eeb 0% l\u00ean 80% ch\u1ec9 trong h\u01a1n 30 ph\u00fat. V\u1edbi gi\u00e1 33.470 USD t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, Mazda MX-30 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p><strong>9. Mini Cooper SE (177 km)<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/bmw-mini-cooper-se-front-quarter-178.jpg\" data-desc=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" data-index=\"1\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/bmw-mini-cooper-se-front-quarter-178.jpg\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1ea3nh 2\" data-image-id=\"3324293\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"397\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/bmw-mini-cooper-se-front-quarter-178.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Mini Cooper SE l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n trong \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb. N\u00f3 cung c\u1ea5p tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e1i th\u00fa v\u1ecb, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i t\u1eeb 1-2 ng\u00e0y trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 m\u1edbi c\u1ea7n s\u1ea1c \u0111i\u1ec7n. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed9 s\u1ea1c nhanh 50 kilowatt gi\u00fap Mini Cooper SE t\u0103ng 80% dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 trong n\u1eeda gi\u1edd. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed7 xe g\u1ea7n c\u00e1c khu chung c\u01b0 c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Chi\u1ebfc xe c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 34.225 USD.<\/p>\n<p><strong>8. Nissan Leaf (239,7 km)<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-nissan-leaf-8250.jpg\" data-desc=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" data-index=\"2\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-nissan-leaf-8250.jpg\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1ea3nh 3\" data-image-id=\"3324292\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"391\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-nissan-leaf-8250.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>L\u00e0 m\u1eabu EV b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nissan, Leaf \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh ti\u1ebfng kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong su\u1ed1t 12 n\u0103m. Trong phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Nissan Leaf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi hai bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3. Trong \u0111\u00f3, g\u00f3i trang tr\u00ed &#8216;S&#8217; ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7.<\/p>\n<p>Trong khi bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 Nissan S ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 27.400 USD c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng 149 d\u1eb7m (239,7 km), SV Plus c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 35.800 USD, cung c\u1ea5p t\u1ea7m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng 212 d\u1eb7m (341,1 km). H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfc xe v\u1eabn mang l\u1ea1i n\u00e9t tinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng.<\/p>\n<p><strong>7. Hyundai Ioniq 5 (354 km)<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-hyundai-ioniq-5-exterior12-761.jpg\" data-desc=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" data-index=\"3\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-hyundai-ioniq-5-exterior12-761.jpg\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1ea3nh 4\" data-image-id=\"3324290\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"530\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-hyundai-ioniq-5-exterior12-761.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Chi\u1ebfc SUV ch\u1ea1y \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u1ee1 trung Hyundai Ioniq 5 mang n\u00e9t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng an to\u00e0n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t chi\u1ebfc xe mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c sang tr\u1ecdng nh\u1edd m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng tin gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed v\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc xe sang tr\u1ecdng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u1edbi 220 d\u1eb7m (354 km) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p trong ch\u00ednh bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf, Ioniq 5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3ng 1 tu\u1ea7n trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, chi\u1ebfc xe n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ea1c \u0111i\u1ec7n cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb kh\u00e1c. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 39.950 USD t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, Ioniq 5 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<\/p>\n<p><strong>6. Polestar 2 (360,4 km)<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2021-volvo-polestar-2-2-cropped-802.jpg\" data-desc=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" data-index=\"4\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2021-volvo-polestar-2-2-cropped-802.jpg\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1ea3nh 5\" data-image-id=\"3324288\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"375\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2021-volvo-polestar-2-2-cropped-802.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Polestar 2 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac, chi\u1ebfc xe v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a th\u00edch b\u1edfi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1eaft m\u1eaft v\u00e0 trang b\u1ecb c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng cung c\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng. M\u1eabu EV n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng tin gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean Google r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 th\u00fa v\u1ecb. Bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 mang t\u00ean Standard Range Pilot cung c\u1ea5p ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng 224 d\u1eb7m (360,4 km). Chi\u1ebfc xe c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 50.000 USD t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<\/p>\n<p><strong>5. Kia EV6 (373,3 km)<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-kia-ev6-cropped-5737.jpg\" data-desc=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" data-index=\"5\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-kia-ev6-cropped-5737.jpg\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1ea3nh 6\" data-image-id=\"3324291\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"375\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-kia-ev6-cropped-5737.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Kia \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi trong EV6, tung ra m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe t\u1eadp trung v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, v\u1ebb b\u1ec1 ngo\u00e0i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o. EV6 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec7n E-GMP v\u1edbi Hyundai Ioniq 5. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ngay c\u1ea3 \u1edf phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n, Kia EV6 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh 232 d\u1eb7m (373,3 km).<\/p>\n<p>EV6 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi pin 58 kWh, t\u1ea1o ra c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 167 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn 258 lb-ft (349,8 Nm). Nh\u1edd s\u1ea1c DC c\u1ef1c nhanh, EV6 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ea1c t\u1eeb 10% \u0111\u1ebfn 80% ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 20 ph\u00fat. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111ang v\u1ed9i, Kia EV6 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng th\u00eam ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 70 d\u1eb7m (112,6 km) ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n s\u1ea1c 10 ph\u00fat. Chi\u1ebfc xe c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 ni\u00eam y\u1ebft 40.900 USD t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<\/p>\n<p><strong>4. Kia Niro (384,6 km)<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/kia2-3135.jpg\" data-desc=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" data-index=\"6\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/kia2-3135.jpg\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1ea3nh 7\" data-image-id=\"3324294\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"500\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/kia2-3135.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Kia cung c\u1ea5p chi\u1ebfc crossover Niro EV v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u01a1n, t\u1ea1o ra c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 201 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn g\u1ea7n 300 lb-ft (406,7 Nm). Pin 64 kWh trong Kia Niro \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n 380 km. Chi\u1ebfc xe s\u1edf h\u1eefu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 s\u1ea1c nhanh DC, v\u1eabn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng xa th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<p>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0m cho Niro tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 39.900 USD c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. Niro \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi g\u00f3i b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh 10 n\u0103m\/100.000 d\u1eb7m, thu\u1ed9c m\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac.<\/p>\n<p><strong>3. Volkswagen ID.4 (410,3 km)<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/volkswagen-id4-609.jpg\" data-desc=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" data-index=\"7\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/volkswagen-id4-609.jpg\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1ea3nh 8\" data-image-id=\"3324297\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"393\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/volkswagen-id4-609.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Volkswagen ID.4 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng ho\u1eb7c r\u1ebb ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c xe \u0111i\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c trong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 Hyundai Kona ho\u1eb7c Nissan Leaf. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n thu\u1ebf li\u00ean bang Hoa K\u1ef3 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c 7.500 USD, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn ID.4 bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 Pro gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 c\u00f2n 38.795 USD.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, ID.4 cung c\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng b\u00ean trong khoang n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng sang tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Polestar 2 hay EV6. Trong khi bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7u sau, chi\u1ebfc xe v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc EV gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng cung c\u1ea5p ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng 255 d\u1eb7m (410,3 km) trong c\u00e1c bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.<\/p>\n<p><strong>2. Hyundai Kona Electric (415,2 km)<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/kona-electric-415.jpg\" data-desc=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" data-index=\"8\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/kona-electric-415.jpg\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1ea3nh 9\" data-image-id=\"3324295\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"422\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/kona-electric-415.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Kia Niro EV, Hyundai Kona hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2022. Chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng nh\u1edd v\u00e0o ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 415,2 km, cung c\u1ea5p t\u00ednh thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh uy t\u00edn. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111\u1ea1t 201 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c. N\u00f3 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 34.000 USD t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<\/p>\n<p><strong>1. Chevrolet Bolt EUV (416,8 km)<\/strong><\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-chevrolet-bolt-euv-front-angle-on-road-4487.jpg\" data-desc=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" data-index=\"9\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-chevrolet-bolt-euv-front-angle-on-road-4487.jpg\" alt=\"Lo\u1ea1t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh d\u00e2n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1ea3nh 10\" data-image-id=\"3324289\" data-width=\"750\" data-height=\"398\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/gn-jwcajw\/2022_09_26\/2022-chevrolet-bolt-euv-front-angle-on-road-4487.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Bolt EUV s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i SuperCruise c\u1ee7a GM. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc Chevy. C\u1eeda s\u1ed5 tr\u1eddi to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh khi\u1ebfn Bolt EUV tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi &#8220;ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em&#8221; Chevrolet Bolt EV. V\u1edbi 33.500 USD, chi\u1ebfc xe l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu EV c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 &#8220;m\u1ec1m&#8221; nh\u1ea5t trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc EV d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 khi ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf ch\u00fang l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, d\u00e0n xe \u0111i\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u00f2n mang gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh &#8220;ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng&#8221; nh\u01b0ng di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u00e0i cho m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13633,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1,30],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13832"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13832"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13832\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":13833,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13832\/revisions\/13833"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/13633"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=13832"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=13832"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=13832"},{"taxonomy":"yst_prominent_words","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/yst_prominent_words?post=13832"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}